        "url": "/groups/G0050",
        "description": "<a href='/groups/G0050'>APT32</a> used Outlook Credential Dumper to harvest credentials stored in Windows registry. <a href='https://www.cybereason.com/blog/operation-cobalt-kitty-apt' target='_blank'>[3]</a> <a href='https://cdn2.hubspot.net/hubfs/3354902/Cybereason%20Labs%20Analysis%20Operation%20Cobalt%20Kitty.pdf' target='_blank'>[4]</a>"
      },
