        "description": "<a href='/software/S1022'>IceApple</a> can harvest credentials from local and remote host registries. <a href='https://www.crowdstrike.com/wp-content/uploads/2022/05/crowdstrike-iceapple-a-novel-internet-information-services-post-exploitation-framework.pdf' target='_blank'>[5]</a>"
